{"tid":1842421,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳門宣布關閘拱北口岸人車通關時間縮短3小時","createTime":"2020-01-25T16:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T16:27:43.000Z","uid":325565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02f665cc6320618e13c9cdb3952a250f45d58027","tid":1842421,"uid":325565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"澳門今次真係係要讚！<br />\n香港人才仲要多過澳門，但香港真係要收皮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府宣佈，因應新型肺炎防疫形勢，連接珠海的關閘拱北口岸，人車的通關時間都會縮短3個小時，改為早上6時到晚上10時，直至另行通知。其他接連珠海或香港的口岸，通關時間暫時維持不變。澳門政府表示，會密切留意和監察疫情發展，及時採取應變措施。<br />\n<br />\n澳門關閘是與珠海人流最密集的一個口岸，本月11日先曾經刷新單日近50萬人次出入境的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504833-20200125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504833-20200125.htm&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8880ca70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504833-20200125.htm&h=6b499b57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504833-20200125.htm</a><br />\n2020-01-25 HKT 21:19"},{"pid":"eeffef3d6778228af0656074c2450707a08d905d","tid":1842421,"uid":280886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【最直接有效既封關方法】係入境、海關、航空業罷工！有冇得唸？</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE2y8jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE2y8jG.jpg&h=6e3002bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得可行既幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}